<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.3">
<l>vaṇṇanalmaṇi yummarakata mumaḻuttini ḻaleḻun</l>
<l>tiṇṇaicūḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūrttiru mālavaṉtiru nāmaṅka</l>
<l>ḷeṇṇakkaṇṭaviral kaḷāliṟaippoḻu tumeṇṇaki lātupō</l>
<l>yuṇṇakkaṇṭa tamūttaivāyoṭu kavaḷamuntukiṉ ṟārkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr, surrounded by verandas erected in the shade,</l>
<l rend="indent">inlaid with emeralds and sapphire of fine hue,</l>
<l>there are those who,</l>
<l rend="indent">with the fingers used to count the holy names of Tirumāl,</l>
<l>go [about] unable to think [of His names] for even an instant,</l>
<l rend="indent">use [them] to eat, pushing rice balls into their filthy mouths.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
